DESCRIPTION:Join us for Improv Happy Hour—where comedy is unscripted\, unpr
	edictable\, and unbelievably fun! From movie mashups to literary spoofs an
	d bold\, experimental comedy\, our quick-thinking performers turn your sug
	gestions into hilarious scenes on the spot. This family-friendly show at t
	he iconic Gum Wall in Pike Place Market guarantees a night of laughter\, s
	urprises\, and improv magic you won’t forget. Bring your wildest ideas\, y
	our loudest laughs\, and get ready for a one-of-a-kind comedy experience—b
	ecause at Improv Happy Hour\, anything can happen (and usually does)! Buy 
